item.title: CVE-2023-24479|2024-08-02T10:56:04.167Z -- yifan -- yf325
item.description: An authentication bypass vulnerability exists in the httpd nvram.cgi functionality of Yifan YF325 v1.0_20221108. A specially crafted network request can lead to arbitrary command execution. An attacker can send a network request to trigger this vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2023-31272|2024-08-02T14:53:30.723Z -- yifan -- yf325
